ދެއްގެ ކުޑަކުދިންނާއި އާންމުންވަނި ޒިޔާރަތް ކޮށްފައެވެ.</p><div class=\"medium-insert-images medium-insert-images-grid medium-insert-active\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.4285em; font-size: 1rem;\"></span><figure>    <img src=\"http://badha.rashoveshi.mv/uploads/post/squareMedium_5WCBKhQtfNv6PeI9sSIu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-photoname=\"5WCBKhQtfNv6PeI9sSIu.jpg\" data-photoid=\"17\">        </figure><figure>    <img src=\"http://badha.rashoveshi.mv/uploads/post/squareMedium_n95ZYSyJfwBEPrXsz8SH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-photoname=\"n95ZYSyJfwBEPrXsz8SH.jpg\" data-photoid=\"18\">        </figure><figure>    <img src=\"http://badha.rashoveshi.mv/uploads/post/squareMedium_CVbPW7hUpsRJpT6ATE9A.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-photoname=\"CVbPW7hUpsRJpT6ATE9A.jpg\" data-photoid=\"19\">        </figure></div><p><span style=\"line-height: 1.4285em; font-size: 1rem;\">މިއީ ނަސްރުގެ</span><span style=\"font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.4285em;\">&nbsp;ދުވަސް ފާހަގަ ކުރުމުގެ ގޮތުން ފުވައްމުލަކުގައި މިފަދަ ފޮޓޯ މައުރަޒެއް ބެއްވި ފުރަތަމަ ފަހަރެވެ.</span></p><p>ފޮޓޯ މައުރަޒުގެ އިތުރުންވެސް ނަސްރުގެ ދުވަސް ފާހަގަ ކުރުމުގެ ގޮތުން ފުވައްމުލަކުގައި ތަފާތު ހަރަކާތްތަކެއް ހިންގުމަށް އެމް.އެން.ޑީ.އެފްއިން އަންނަނީ ތައްޔާރުވަމުންނެވެ.&nbsp;</p>','[{\"type\":\"text\",\"source\":\"\\u0782\\u07a6\\u0790\\u07b0\\u0783\\u07aa\\u078e\\u07ac \\u078b\\u07aa\\u0788\\u07a6\\u0790\\u07b0 \\u078a\\u07a7\\u0780\\u07a6\\u078e\\u07a6 \\u0786\\u07aa\\u0783\\u07aa\\u0789\\u07aa\\u078e\\u07ac \\u078e\\u07ae\\u078c\\u07aa\\u0782\\u07b0 \\u078a\\u07aa\\u0788\\u07a6\\u0787\\u07b0\\u0789\\u07aa\\u078d\\u07a6\\u0786\\u07aa\\u078e\\u07a6\\u0787\\u07a8 \\u0780\\u07a8\\u0782\\u07b0\\u078e\\u07a7 \\u0780\\u07a6\\u0783\\u07a6\\u0786\\u07a7\\u078c\\u07b0\\u078c\\u07a6\\u0787\\u07b0 \\u0789\\u07a8\\u0787\\u07a6\\u078b\\u07aa \\u0790\\u07a8\\u078a\\u07a6\\u0787\\u07a8\\u0782\\u07b0 \\u078a\\u07a6\\u0781\\u07a6\\u0787\\u07a8\\u078a\\u07a8\\u0787\\u07ac\\u0788\\u07ac. \"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"source\":\"\\u0789\\u07a8 \\u0799\\u07a6\\u0783\\u0